arStrings.szText: When the Mother of Sanctuary re-enters her world, it will change. But in the end, we will remain. We will survive.
Rathma writes that when Inarius discovered Lilith's plan to overthrow the so-called natural order, he sealed her away.
For thousands of years, Lilith has sought to elevate us out of this cycle. Has fought to secure us our birthright: Sanctuary.
